## donations.js

**Summary:** Legacy controller (`DonationsLayout`) registered on the `TuyoTools` module. An empty layout controller that serves as the parent controller for the donations section layout, providing scope inheritance for child donation views.

**Dependencies:**
- app/app/app/app.js — registers controller on root `TuyoTools` module

**Tags:** legacy, controller, donations, layout

**Implementation:** app/app/scripts/controllers/layouts/donations.js
